skill.name: The Darkin Blade
skill.desc:
On cast, cycle through one of the following abilities:

Slash in a line, dealing 110/210/2500(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to enemies hit and 20% Sundering them for 4 seconds.

Swipe in a cone, dealing 132/252/3000(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to enemies hit and knocking them up for 1 second.

Slam on target, dealing 176/336/4000(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage in a 1 hex circle. Targets below 15% max Health are executed.

skill.name: Fox-Fire
skill.desc:
Fire 3 flames at target, each dealing 82/125/195(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage. Every 3rd cast, fire 9 flames split between the target and up to 2 nearby enemies.

If there are nearby enemies, dash away.

skill.name: Lacerate
skill.desc:
Swipe and dash around target, dealing 50/75/350(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to enemies in the path. Then slam chains on target, dealing 158/236/1103(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage in a line. If any enemies are killed, immediately recast this ability, dealing 80% damage.

The slam deals 40/40/100% more damage to Tanks.

skill.name: Frostbite
skill.desc:
Fire an ice shard at target that deals 325/455/650(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage. If they are Chilled, the damage Critically Strikes.

Chill: Reduce Attack Speed

skill.name: Enraged Inferno
skill.desc:
Erupt the entire battlefield in flames, permanently Burning and Wounding all enemies and dealing 1500/2250/8000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to each of them over 45 seconds.

Annie's max Mana is reduced by 140 for the rest of combat. Subsquent casts launch a fireball at target that deals 240/360/3000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage.

Burn: Deal 1% of the target's max Health as true damage every second
Wound: Reduce healing received by 33%

skill.name: Incendiary Onslaught
skill.desc:
Start with Infernum equipped. On cast, switch to Severum for 8(%i:scaleAP%) attacks.

Infernum: Attacks hit 3 enemies and apply 30% Sunder for 6 seconds.
Severum: Gain 200% Attack Speed and 10% Omnivamp. Attacks are replaced with swipes that deal 70/105/175(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage.

Sunder: Reduce Armor

skill.name: True Ice Arrow
skill.desc:
Fire an arrow at target that deals 155/225/340(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to them and 51/74/112(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) damage to adjacent enemies. Targets below 30% max Health take true damage instead. 30% Chill all enemies hit for 3 seconds.

Bloodsworn Bond: When you field Ashe and Tryndamere, your strongest copies permanently increase their power on kill.
Bloodsworn Bond: Attacks fire a bonus arrow for every 10% Attack Damage granted to Tryndamere by Bloodsworn Bond. These arrows deal 3/4/6(%i:TFTBaseAD%) physical damage. (Current Bonus Arrows: ?).

Chill: Reduce Attack Speed

skill.name: Punish the Unworthy
skill.desc:
Passive: Gain 30% Omnivamp and grant Noxians 0/3/3% Damage Amp. Every 2 attacks, swipe twice, dealing a total of 150/225/340(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies in a 1 hex radius and grant Noxians 0/3/3% stacking Damage Amp until the end of combat.

Active: Split 900(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage between enemies within 3 hexes over 2.5 seconds.

skill2.name: Unleash Carnage
skill2.desc: Passive: Gain 30% Omnivamp. Every 2 attacks, deal 150/225/340(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies within 1 hex.

skill3.name: Punish the Unworthy
skill3.desc: Passive: Gain 30% Omnivamp and grant Noxians 3% Damage Amp. Every 2 attacks, swipe twice, dealing a total of 150/225/340(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies in a 1 hex radius and grant Noxians 3% stacking Damage Amp until the end of combat.

skill4.name: Demonic Aura
skill4.desc:
Passive: Gain 30% Omnivamp and grant Noxians 3% Damage Amp. Every 2 attacks, swipe twice, dealing a total of 150/225/340(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies in a 1 hex radius and grant Noxians 3% stacking Damage Amp until the end of combat.

Active: Split 850(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage between enemies within 3 hexes over 2.5 seconds.

skill5.name: Bringer of Ruin
skill5.desc:
Passive: Gain 30% Omnivamp and grant Noxians 0/3/3% Damage Amp. Every 2 attacks, swipe twice, dealing a total of 150/225/340(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies in a 1 hex radius and grant Noxians 0/3/3% stacking Damage Amp until the end of combat. After 10 seconds of combat, devour ALL units.

Active: Deal 850(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies within 3 hexes over 2.5 seconds.

skill.name: The Skies Descend
skill.desc:
Passive: For every 250 ability damage dealt to enemies in player combat, gain Stardust. Stardust makes The Skies Descend more powerful. (Current Stardust: ?)

Active: Crash a star on target, dealing 480/800/5000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage in a 2 hex radius.

Stardust Upgrades:
25: Create a shockwave that deals 100/150/1000(%i:scaleAP%) additional magic damage in a 3 Hex radius.
60: The star crash deals 15% more damage.
140: Shockwave increases to a 4 hex radius.
200: Knock up targets in the star crash for 1.5 seconds.
300: Shockwave increases to 10 radius.
550: The star crash deals 33% bonus true damage.
800: Also call down a meteor storm that deals 500/750/9999(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage split between living enemies.
1444: Summon a black hole at the epicenter, instantly killing enemies within.

skill.name: Arise!
skill.desc:
Passive: After witnessing 3 attacks from Azir, Sand Soldiers deal 100/150/3000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to their target.

Active: Summon a Sand Soldier near target and command them to strike. If 2 Soldiers are already out, they all immediately deal 70/105/5000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage instead.

skill.name: Stand Guard
skill.desc: Does not move or attack. This unit dies when the Emperor dies.

skill.name: Traveler's Call
skill.desc: Launch 6 Meeps at nearby enemies that deal 130/185/255(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage. Add an additional Meep for each 3-star unit on your board. (Total Meeps: ?)

skill.name: Wrath of the Void
skill.desc:
Passive: Immune to Crowd Control effects. Attacks deal damage in a line on target. If no enemies are in range, dash to the next one and knock up adjacent enemies on arrival.

While in the Void Rift, erupt a tentacle below a random enemy every 3 seconds that knocks them up for 1.5 seconds.

Active: Slam and erect spikes in a 2 hex circle, dealing 280/420/20500(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to enemies hit. Then over 3 seconds, spit 10 globs of acid that deal 112/189/10250(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage.

skill.name: Endless Banquet
skill.desc:
Passive: On takedown, gain 100/100/200% Attack Speed that decays over 3 seconds.

Active: Deal 150/225/900(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage in a 2 hex radius and transform for the rest of combat.

While transformed, gain 33%/33%/133%(%i:scaleAP%) Attack Speed, 33% max Health, and increased Move Speed. Attacks deal 15/25/100 bonus true damage, increased by 3/5/30 for each time the same enemy is hit.

skill.name: Static Field
skill.desc: Gain 400/480/600(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 4 seconds and deal 56/84/126(%i:scaleMR%) magic damage to all enemies within 1 hex.

skillHero.name: Rocket Fist
skillHero.desc: Pull the furthest enemy within 5(%i:scaleRange%) hexes, preferring enemies with less items. Then, gain 60%(%i:scaleAP%) Attack Speed for 3 attacks. These attacks deal 160/240/360(%i:scaleAD%) bonus physical damage.

skill.name: Golem Smash
skill.desc: Slam the target dealing 300/480/750(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage.

skill.name: Unbreakable Frost
skill.desc:
Raise shield for 4 seconds, gaining 55%/55%/90%(%i:scaleAP%) Durability and redirecting projectiles to towards Braum instead. When hit, deal 27/43/1245(%i:scaleArmor%%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to nearby enemies and 30% Chill them for 2 seconds.

Chill: Reduce Attack Speed

skill.name: Blood Frenzy
skill.desc: Leap to the furthest enemy within 2 hexes. For 4 seconds gain increased Move Speed, 25% Attack Damage, and 300%/300%/350%(%i:scaleAP%) decaying Attack Speed.

skill.name: Seismic Slam
skill.desc:
Passive: Immune to crowd control effects. Attacks briefly knock up the target and deal 50% damage in a 1 hex radius around them.

Active: Slam the ground, dealing 186/265/1617(%i:scaleHealth%%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to ALL enemies, reduced by 15% for each hex from the center (down to 40%.) If this is the first time they've been hit by Seismic Slam this combat, knock them up for up to 1.75 seconds. 12 rocks fall around the battlefield, each dealing 220/405/700(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to enemies hit.

skill.name: Ace in the Hole
skill.desc: Fire a bullet towards the farthest enemy, dealing 515/775/1205(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to the first enemy it hits. If they die, the bullet ricochets, dealing excess damage to the next enemy hit.

skill.name: Rupture
skill.desc: Restore 200/225/400(%i:scaleAP%) Health and rupture a 2 hex circle beneath target. After a brief delay, enemies within are knocked up for 1.5 seconds and take 88/152/248(%i:scaleHealth%%i:scaleAP%) magic damage.

skill.name: Decimate
skill.desc:
Restore 315/463/717(%i:scaleHealth%%i:scaleAP%) Health and spin, dealing 90/135/210(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to adjacent enemies and applying a stack of Hemorrhage that deals 12/18/30(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage each second for 5 seconds.

If an enemy with Hemorrhage drops below 8% Health, slam on them, instantly killing them. (Each stack increases the execute threshold by 5%)

skill.name: Lunar Rush
skill.desc:
Passive: Ability damage from your strongest Leona and strongest Diana marks enemies as Moonlit, reducing their damage by 10%.

Active: Gain 100/175/300(%i:scaleAP%) Shield. Unleash a bolt of lunar energy at the farthest non-Moonlit enemy within 4 hexes, dealing 125/190/600(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage. Then, dash to all Moonlit enemies, dealing 140/210/1350(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to them.

skill.name: Spinning Axes
skill.desc:
Passive: If Draven has an empowered axe in hand, his next attack will throw it. On takedown, gain an Adoration stack, doubled if Draven or Darius scored the kill. Every 11 Adoration stacks grants 1/3/5 Gold.

Active: Spin an empowered axe that replaces his basic attack and deals 130/185/315(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage and returns to Draven after hitting an enemy.

skill.name: Maximum Dosage
skill.desc: Bulk up for 5 seconds. While bulked, restore 114/177/275(%i:scaleHealth%%i:scaleAP%) Health every second and attacks deal 105/171/291(%i:scaleHealth%%i:scaleAD%) physical damage.

skill.name: On Duty!
skill.desc: The Training Dummy cannot move or attack. It is also dressed like a devilishly handsome Yordle.

skill.name: Parallel Convergence
skill.desc:
Create a 1 hex zone around the target that lasts 3 seconds. The next 3 attacks deal 150/225/340(%i:scaleAP%) bonus magic damage.

When the zone ends, it deals 130/195/295(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage + 10% of the target's damage taken during the duration to all enemies in the zone.

skill.name: Crowstorm
skill.desc: Teleport into a large cluster of enemies within 2 hexes and Stun them for 1.25 seconds. Begin losing 22 mana per second. While casting, deal 100/150/6666(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage per second to all enemies within a 2 hex radius. The closest 2 enemies take 33% more damage.

skill.name: Playful Trickster
skill.desc: Become briefly untargetable, then jump to the farthest enemy within 4 hexes, avoiding Tanks and Fighters, and deal 75/115/450(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to adjacent enemies. For the next 4 attacks, gain 100% Attack Speed and deal 50/75/600(%i:scaleAP%) bonus magic damage on hit.

skill.name: Ancient Sentinel
skill.desc: Built before anyone can remember, these frozen statues line the bridges above the Howling Abyss, eternally vigilant.

skill.name: Inspirational Might
skill.desc:
Passive: Every 3rd attack deals 247/370/5850(%i:scaleMR%) magic damage in a circle around the target.

Active: Dash into the largest group of units and inspire all allies within 2 hexes, granting them 500/600/2000(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 4 seconds. Then crash down, dealing 325/488/3900(%i:scaleMR%%i:scaleArmor%) bonus magic damage to all enemies with 2 hexes.

skill.name: Powder Kegs
skill.desc: Toss barrels at the 3 nearest enemies and detonate them. They deal 200/300/475(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) damage, reduced by 25% for each barrel in the chain. Barrels reduce their target's Armor by 10, increased to 20 if the damage critically strikes.

skill.name: Judgment
skill.desc: Spin for 3 seconds, gaining 50/50/80% Durability and healing for 370/516/1589(%i:scaleHealth%%i:scaleAP%) over the duration. Each second, deal 100/150/1700(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to adjacent enemies and reduce their Armor and Magic Resistance by 5.

skill.name: Collateral Damage
skill.desc:
Passive: Attacks fire in a cone on target, dealing 45% damage to other enemies hit.

Active: Fire an explosive shell at target, dealing 200/300/450(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage split among enemies in a 1 hex circle.

Partners in Crime: When you field Graves and Twisted Fate, both gain bonuses.
Partners in Crime: Your strongest Twisted Fate's ability marks targets for your strongest Graves. Graves gains 2% stacking Attack Speed when attacking marked targets.

skill.name: Snip Snip!
skill.desc: Dash around target and snip 5(%i:scaleSouls%) times, dealing 50/75/120(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to them and 25/35/60(%i:scaleAP%) damage to all other enemies in a cone.

skill.name: Tentacle Smash
skill.desc: Restore 249/328/439(%i:scaleHealth%%i:scaleAP%) Health and slam a tentacle, dealing 180/270/405(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to enemies in a line.

skillHero.name: Leap of Faith
skillHero.desc: Deal 242/363/550(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to the current target, increased by 60% against Tanks. If the target dies, immediately recast dealing 75% damage.

skill.name: Demacian Standard
skill.desc: Gain 350/425/500(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 4 seconds. Grant all allies 20%/25%/50%(%i:scaleAP%) Attack Speed for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Curtain Call
skill.desc: For the next 4 attacks, set Attack Speed to 1, gain infinite range and replace attacks with a cannon shot. Cannon shots deal 160/237/359(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage. The 4th shot deals 144% more damage.

skill.name: Switcheroo!
skill.desc: Passive: After attacking 18/18/16 times, switch to Fishbones. While equipped, attacks are replaced with 3 rockets that target random enemies and deal 54/81/134(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage.

skill.name: Icathian Rain
skill.desc: Dash away from all enemies, then fire 15/15/25 missiles split across the 4 nearest enemies. Each missile deals 45/72/170(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage.

skill2.name: Supercharge
skill2.desc: Gain 20/20/100% Attack Speed for the rest of combat. For 5 seconds, attacks are empowered to deal 60/90/500(%i:scaleAP%) bonus magic damage. Every 5th empowered attack deals 250/400/1600(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage instead.

skill.name: Endless Rend
skill.desc: Summon 20(%i:scaleSouls%) spears split among the 4 nearest enemies. After a brief delay, they each impale their target, dealing 35/53/465(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage and reducing Armor by 1.

skill.name: Slicing Maelstrom
skill.desc: Gain 600/700/900(%i:scaleAP%) Shield and summon storm of lightning. 6 waves of bolts hit enemies within, dealing 120/180/290(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage over 3 seconds. The first 3 targets to be struck by 3 bolts are Stunned for 1.5 seconds. Multiple Stuns on the same enemy have 50% effectiveness.

skill.name: Lamb's Respite
skill.desc:
Dash, then create a 2-hex radius zone for 2.5/2.5/99 seconds that shields allies within for 350/750/10000(%i:scaleAP%) health for the zone's duration. While active, double current Attack Speed and on attack, fire a secondary arrow at a nearby enemy that deals 25/38/999(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage.

When the zone ends, heal all allies for 8%(%i:scaleAP%) of damage dealt while it was up and dash away.

skill.name: You & Me!
skill.desc:
Passive: Yuumi joins your strongest Kobuko. Every 3 seconds, she alternates between healing the lowest Health ally for 140/180/240(%i:scaleAP%) Health or granting 25/33/50% Attack Speed to the ally who has dealt the most damage for 4 seconds.

Active: Dance, restoring 294/445/669(%i:scaleHealth%%i:scaleAP%) Health over 3 seconds.

skill.name: Caustic Spittle
skill.desc: Deal 140/200/300(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to target and reduce their Armor and Magic Resist by 8/10/15. Adjacent enemies are dealt 50% of the damage and effect.

skill.name: Distortions
skill.desc: Summon 3 dashing mirror images that strike the target and up to 2 other nearby enemies. The target takes 300/450/700(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage and is Stunned for 1 second, while other units hit take 180/270/450(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage.

skill.name: Solar Flare
skill.desc:
Passive: Reduce instances of incoming damage by 15/30/60(%i:scaleAP%). Your strongest Leona grants your strongest Diana 3 Ability Power every second she survives.

Active: Call down sun beams on the 3 nearest enemies, Stunning them for 1 second and dealing 80/120/200(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage. Wound and 1% Burn them for 4 seconds.

Wound: Reduce healing received by 33%
Burn: Deal 1% of the target's max Health as true damage every second

skill.name: Frozen Tomb
skill.desc:
Encase target in ice, Stunning them for 1 second and dealing 315/475/2800(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage. All enemies within 2 hexes of them split 415/625/2800(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage. If the target dies, shards fly out and split excess damage between the 2 nearest enemies.

Chilled enemies take 12% more damage from this ability.

Chill: Reduce Attack Speed

skill.name: Piltover Tussle
skill.desc: Gain 700/800/1000(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 4 seconds. Charge and knock the target backwards, Stunning them and units hit for 1.25 seconds and dealing 150/225/360(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to them. After charging, force nearby enemies to target this unit.

skill.name: The Culling
skill.desc: Fire 12/12/42(%i:scaleAS%) shots towards target. Each shot explodes on the first enemy hit, dealing 83/132/900(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to all nearby enemies.

skill2.name: Dawning Shadow
skill2.desc: Fire a massive beam at the furthest enemy. Enemies hit take 230/350/2000(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage, reduced by 8% per enemy hit, up to 40%. Allies hit gain 180/270/2000(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Whimsy
skill.desc: Deal 285/425/635(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to target and make them dance for 2 seconds. The projectile then bounces to the nearest target, dealing 120/180/270(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage.

skill.name: Final Spark
skill.desc: Fire a ball of light at the most enemies, dealing 30/45/100(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to the first 2 enemies hit and Rooting them for 1 second. Then fire a beam, dealing 330/500/1600(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies hit by the ball and 90/135/900(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to all other enemies hit.

skill.name: Void Swarm
skill.desc: Summon 2 Voidlings that each attack a nearby enemy 8 times. Each attack deals 29/43/68(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage.

skill.name: Placeholder Name
skill.desc: Placeholder Tooltip

skill.name: Radiant Eclipse
skill.desc:
Passive: While gaining Mana, throw out 2 radiant orbs that orbit around target. They deal 65/100/150(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage in a 1 hex radius and drain 1 Mana from enemies hit each second. After draining 235 mana, gain a random Radiant Item. (?/235)

Active: Detonate orbs on target, causing a 3 hex radius explosion that deals 1000/1500/10000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to them and 400/600/10000(%i:scaleAP%) damage to all other enemies hit.

skill.name: Ultra Mega Fire Kick!!!
skill.desc: Launch a fuemigo at target that bounces 3 times, dealing 190/285/445(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies hit. The last bounce deals 160/240/375(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies in a 1 hex radius.

skill.name: Heartbreaker
skill.desc:
Passive: Attacks ricochet to the highest current Health enemy, dealing 50/50/100% damage.

Active: Fire waves of bullets that land on the 2 nearest enemies. The first wave deals 245/370/3070(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage and the rest deal 98/148/2456(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage. Every 3rd cast, increase the number of waves by 1.

skill.name: Fury of the Sands
skill.desc: Steal 485/620/3000(%i:scaleAP%) Health split between the 4/4/8 nearest enemies. For 8 seconds, gain 30 Armor and Magic Resist and deal 23/41/583(%i:scaleHealth%) magic damage to adjacent enemies each second.

skill.name: Titan's Wrath
skill.desc:
Passive: Every 4 seconds and on cast, the next attack deals damage in a 1 hex circle and deals 45/68/108(%i:scaleMR%) bonus magic damage.

Active: Gain 465/562/717(%i:scaleHealth%%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Pop Blossom
skill.desc:
Leap at target and gain 400/475/600(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 4 seconds. Slam down after a brief delay, dealing 80/120/180(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies within two hexes and 20% Chilling them for 2 seconds.

Chill: Reduce Attack Speed

skill.name: Relentless Pounce
skill.desc:
Jump on an adjacent enemy with the lowest health, then deal 320/500/2000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to them and 100/150/600(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to adjacent enemies. If any die, cast again, dealing 70% damage.

Tanks take 60% more damage from this ability and Fighters take 30% more.

skill.name: Command: Protect
skill.desc:
Send the Ball to target, dealing 220/330/500(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage and splitting 120/180/300(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage among enemies within a 1 hex circle.

Then grant 60/90/130(%i:scaleAP%) Shield to the two lowest Health allies for 3 seconds.

skill.name: Call of the Forge
skill.desc:
Summon an elemental from behind the farthest enemy. It 20% Chills enemies hit for 5 seconds and deals 100/150/3000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to them.

When it arrives, headbutt it and redirect it toward another distant enemy, dealing 150/225/4500(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage instead.

Chill: Reduce Attack Speed

skill.name: Piltover Customs Special
skill.desc: Each item equipped to the invention will determine what it does when it fires.

skill.name: Hammer Shock
skill.desc: Gain 330/410/500(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 4 seconds and deal 70/105/165(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to target. After a delay, briefly knock them up and deal the damage again. Bucklers fly out from the target, granting 2 nearby allies 30% of the Shield gained.

skill.name: Clear The Brush
skill.desc: Dash to a nearby hex and swing forward, dealing 180/270/445(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to enemies in a 2-hex line.

skill.name: Burrow
skill.desc: Dash to the furthest enemy within 3 hexes and deal 160/240/360(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to them. The next 3 attacks hit adjacent enemies and deal 110/165/260(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage.

skill.name: Slice and Dice
skill.desc: Dash to the lowest Health enemy within 2 hexes, dealing 80/120/360(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to all enemies in the path. Then slash 4 times, each dealing 55/85/600(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage. Subsquent casts increase the number of slashes by 1.

skill.name: Warp Armor
skill.desc: Gain 300/425/2000 max Health and grow larger. Slam in a 2 Hex circle on the target, dealing 166/269/2428(%i:scaleAP%%i:scaleHealth%) magic damage to enemies hit. For 4 seconds, gain 25%/25%/80%(%i:scaleAP%) Durability + 1% for each enemy targeting this unit.

skill.name: Junkyard Titan
skill.desc: Gain 350/430/550(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 4 seconds. Fire a burst of flames, dealing 72/108/162(%i:scaleArmor%) magic damage in a cone.

skillHero.name: Artillery Barrage
skillHero.desc: Passive: Fire 3(%i:scaleAS%) missiles every second, split between target and up to 2 nearby enemies. Each one deals 32/48/72(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage.

skill.name: Runic Overload
skill.desc:
Release a runic blast, dealing 235/425/1500(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage. It splits in two, dealing 33% of the damage to the closest two enemies. Each secondary blast splits an additional time.

Bilgewater: Blasts explode on impact, dealing 25% of the damage as physical damage to adjacent enemies.
Demacia: Execute targets below 12%(%i:scaleArmor%%i:scaleMR%) Health.
Freljord: Chill targets for 4 seconds and deal 60/108/194(%i:scaleHealth%) bonus true damage.
Ionia: Blasts split an additional time, dealing 50% damage.
Ixtal: Gain a random Region's effect on combat start and every 10 seconds.
Noxus: Blasts now pierce targets, dealing 60% reduced damage per enemy hit.
Piltover: Every third cast is Overcharged, dealing 40% more damage.
Shadow Isles: Increase blast damage by 5%(%i:scaleSouls%).
Shurima: Knock up enemies for 0.5 seconds, with a chance to dredge up Gold or Treasures.
Targon: Heal the lowest Health ally for 10% of the damage dealt.
Void: Ignore 30% of enemies' Armor and Magic Resistance.
Yordle: Shrink targets hit, lowering their damage by 12% percent for 4 seconds.
Zaun: Poison targets, dealing 15/30/500 magic damage 3(%i:scaleAS%) times over 4 seconds.

skill.name: Winter's Wrath
skill.desc:
Gain 525/575/675(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 4 seconds. Strike in a cone and a line. Enemies hit take 70/105/170(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage and are 30% Chilled for 4 seconds. If they are already Chilled, Stun them for 1 second.

Chill: Reduce Attack Speed

skill.name: Grand Encore
skill.desc:
Gain 3 notes. For each one active, deal 35/55/300(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to a nearby enemy.

While holding 12 notes on cast, consume them to project a wave of energy. Allies hit restore 40/80/400(%i:scaleAP%) Health. Enemies hit take 270/405/2200(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage, reduced by 30% for each enemy it's passed through.

skill.name: Infernal Chains
skill.desc: Pull in 2/2/5 of the farthest enemies, then deal 250/450/1500(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage in a 1-hex radius.

skill.name: Five Point Strike
skill.desc: Throw kunai at the current target, dealing 190/285/460(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage.

skill.name: Burst Shield
skill.desc: Blast a cone of fire, dealing 180/270/360(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies in front, then gain a 450/700/1000(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 8 seconds.

skill.name: Voice of Lightning
skill.desc:
Breathe lightning in a line toward the farthest enemy, dealing 225/350/1000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage and Overcharging all enemies hit for 10 seconds.
If an enemy is already Overcharged, consume the effect and deal 50% bonus magic damage.

skill.name: Emperor's Divide
skill.desc: Call forth a wall of soldiers that charge through the current target, dealing 350/550/8888(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage and slowing all enemies hit for 3 seconds. Enemies nearby are knocked back, while enemies farther away are Stunned for 1.5 seconds.

skill.name: Stand Firm
skill.desc: Azir's Sand Guards accompany their Emperor on the battlefield. They don't attack, but they get in the enemy's way.

skill.name: Dragonfire Pillar
skill.desc: After a brief delay, cause the ground under the enemy with the highest current Health to erupt in flames, dealing 200/350/550(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies within a 1-hex radius. Enemies caught in the epicenter are Stunned for 1.5/2/3 seconds.

skill.name: Unbreakable
skill.desc: Gain 70%/75%/85%(%i:scaleAP%) Durability in the direction of the largest cluster of enemies for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Rupture
skill.desc:
Rupture a 2.5-hex radius area around a random enemy, dealing 200/400/1500(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage and Stunning all enemies within for 2/2.5/8 seconds.

Fabled Bonus: Knock up ALL enemies on the board.

skill.name: Fortune's Guillotine
skill.desc: Dunk the current target, dealing 475/715/1000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage. While dunking, become Unstoppable. If the target dies, immediately cast again, dealing 25/20/15% reduced damage.

skill.name: Pale Cascade
skill.desc: Gain a 200/300/450(%i:scaleAP%) Shield over 4 seconds and summon 4/5/6 orbs to orbit. These orbs explode for 80/85/90(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage when they hit an enemy, refreshing the Shield when the final orb explodes.

skill.name: Spider Form
skill.desc:
Transform into a spider, gaining 40%/60%/80%(%i:scaleAP%) maximum Health. Spider Form attacks heal for 40/60/80(%i:scaleAP%) and 35/35/50% Mana Reave the target.

Mana Reave: increase maximum Mana until the next cast

skill.name: Riposte
skill.desc: Enter a defensive stance for 1.5 seconds, becoming immune to damage and enemy Abilities. Afterwards, strike, dealing 250/400/600(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to a nearby enemy and Stunning them for 1/1.5/2 seconds.

skill.name: Provocation Aura
skill.desc: Gain 50% Durability for 3 seconds, Taunting all enemies in a 2-hex radius. At the end of the taunt, send out a pulse of infernal fire, dealing 100/500/1000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies around.

skill.name: Judgement
skill.desc: Spin for 4 seconds, dealing 450/675/1170(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to nearby enemies and reducing incoming magic damage by 80% over the duration.

skill.name: Bladestorm
skill.desc:
Launch a storm of blades in a line at the current target, dealing 150/200/250(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage and Disarming enemies for 2.5/3/5 seconds.

Disarm: Target cannot attack

skill.name: Eye of the Storm
skill.desc: Shield the 2/3/4 lowest-Health allies for 250/275/350(%i:scaleAP%) for 4 seconds. Shielded allies also gain 15/20/25% bonus Attack Damage %i:scaleAD% for that duration.

skill.name: Dragon Strike
skill.desc: Throw a standard near the farthest enemy and pull towards it with a lance, dealing 200/300/500(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies passed through, and Stunning them for 1 second.

skill.name: Counter Strike
skill.desc: Dodge all incoming attacks for 2 seconds, then strike all nearby enemies, dealing 150/250/450(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage and Stunning them for 1.5 seconds.

skill.name: Rend
skill.desc: Passive: Spears remain in the target, each dealing 4%/6%/9%(%i:scaleAP%) of the target's max Health when removed. Spears are removed when doing so would deal lethal damage.

skill.name: Death Lotus
skill.desc:
Channel for 2.5 seconds, throwing knives at 4/5/6 enemies in a 2-hex radius, dealing 345/520/825(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage over the duration and applying Wound for 5 seconds.

Wound: Reduce healing received by 50%

skill.name: Divine Ascension
skill.desc: Ascend, causing attacks to launch waves that deal 80/120/360(%i:scaleAP%) bonus magic damage.

skill.name: Slicing Maelstrom
skill.desc: Summon a storm for 3 seconds, calling down lightning bolts on all enemies every 0.5 second, dealing 350/550/800(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage over the duration. Each enemy struck by 3 lightning bolts is Stunned for 1.5 seconds.

skill.name: Dance of Dread
skill.desc:
Deal 325/490/730(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage and Wound for 5 seconds, while leaping away.

Wound: Reduce healing received by 33%

skill.name: God Fist
skill.desc:
Punch the target, dealing 200/375/1000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage, knocking them back to the edge of the battlefield, and Stunning them for 2/3/10 seconds. Enemies struck by the target take half damage and are also Stunned for 1/1/10 second.

If the target cannot be pushed back further, knock them out of the battlefield, removing them from combat.

If the target survives, dash to them.

skill.name: Wild Growth
skill.desc: Transform a low-Health ally into a giant that Stuns nearby enemies for 1 second. Giant allies gain 400/600/950(%i:scaleAP%) bonus Health for the rest of combat.

skill.name: Bramble Smash
skill.desc:
Smash the ground, sending a shockwave towards the current target that deals 225/350/550(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies hit and Chills them for 3 seconds.

Chill: Reduce Attack Speed by 50%

skill.name: Hallowed Ground
skill.desc: Hallow the ground beneath a random target, dealing 300/475/2000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies within 2.5-hex area over 5 seconds and reducing their Attack Damage by 40/40/50%.

skill.name: Wither
skill.desc:
Wither the enemy with the highest percent Health, dealing 350/550/850(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage over 5 seconds, Chilling them, and slowing their movement speed by 50% for the duration.

Chill: Reduce Attack Speed by 50%

skill.name: Impact Crater
skill.desc:
Cause the ground beneath the target to erupt, knocking them up, Stunning them for 3/4/5 seconds, and dealing 270/400/600(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage.

Fabled Bonus: Also gain a shield that gives 50% Durability for 5 seconds.

Durability: Reduce damage received

skill.name: Blooming Burst
skill.desc:
Throw a seed at a random target that explodes for 150/225/350(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage 3 times. Each explosion affects a bigger area than the last.

Fabled Bonus: The third explosion is empowered, dealing 200% bonus damage.

skill.name: Javelin Toss
skill.desc: Throw a javelin at the farthest enemy, dealing 100/175/270(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage plus 80% more for each hex traveled.

skill.name: Consume
skill.desc: Bite the target, dealing 200/350/500(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage. If the target has less Health, deal an additional 50% and convert it to true damage.

skill.name: Ragnarok
skill.desc: Gain 140/165/340% Attack Speed, become Unstoppable, and cleave attacks in a cone dealing 50%(%i:TFTBaseAD% %i:scaleAP%) physical damage for the rest of combat.

skill.name: Stampede
skill.desc:
Summon an elemental from behind the farthest enemy to travel toward Ornn, Chilling all enemies hit for 3 seconds and dealing 225/400/9999(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage.

If the elemental runs into Ornn, headbutt it, redirecting it toward another distant enemy, Stunning for 2/2.5/15 seconds and dealing 225/400/9999(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to all enemies hit.

Chill: Reduce Attack Speed by 50%

skill.name: Phantom Undertow
skill.desc: Leave a phantom at the current location, then dash behind the farthest enemy. After 1 second, the phantom returns, dealing 150/225/325(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to all enemies it passes through and Stunning them for 1.5/2/2.75 seconds.

skill.name: Year of the Horse
skill.desc: Complete the race to earn special loot! Player combat losses accelerate the race timer by an additional turn.

skill.name: Disarming Diversion
skill.desc:
Dash to the furthest enemy within attack range, Disarming all units passed through for 2/2.5/3 seconds, and Taunting the target. Gain a 400/500/775(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 4 seconds.

Disarm: Target cannot attack

skill.name: Inferno Trigger
skill.desc: Dash away from the current target and become Unstoppable, gaining 100% dodge chance and unleashing 3/3/10(%i:scaleAP%) shots per second at 3/3/9 enemies within 2.5 hexes for 2 seconds. Each shot deals 120/240/1444 physical damage.

skill.name: Firecracker
skill.desc: Throw a giant firecracker at the closest enemy that explodes in a large circle after a 2-second delay. Enemies in the explosion take 150/250/1600(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage and are Stunned for 2.5/2.5/8 seconds.

skill.name: Showstopper
skill.desc: Grab the target and slam them forward, dealing 20%/30%/400%(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage of their max Health and 10%/15%/200%(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage of the slammed enemy's max Health to all other enemies in 3-hex area.

skill.name: Shadow Dash
skill.desc: Dash past the target, gaining a 500/800/4000(%i:scaleAP%) Shield and Taunting all adjacent enemies for 4/4/8 seconds.

skill.name: Dragon's Descent
skill.desc: Dash away from the current target and transform into a dragon, gaining 15/20/25% bonus Health and 15/40/90% Attack Damage %i:scaleAD%. Attacks gain 3 range that deal 125/250/500(%i:scaleAP%) bonus magic damage over 2 seconds.

skill.name: On the Hunt
skill.desc:
Rally allies within 2 hexes, granting them 40%/55%/70%(%i:scaleAP%) Attack Speed for 5 seconds.
Gain 100/150/175% bonus Attack Damage %i:scaleAD% for the duration.

skill.name: Draconic Ascension
skill.desc:
Transform into dragon form for 6 seconds, gaining 60/65/100% max Health and dealing 90/135/1000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage each second to enemies within 2.5/2.5/5 hexes.

While in dragon form, breathe fire in a cone in front every 2 seconds, dealing 175/350/5000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage, burning enemies for 20% of their max Health as true damage over 10 seconds, and Wounding them for the duration.

Wound: Reduce healing received by 33%

skill.name: Thick Skin
skill.desc: Passive: Take 15/25/50(%i:scaleAP%) reduced damage from all sources.

skill.name: Truestrike
skill.desc: Deal 290/490/1350(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to the current target. If this kills them, become Unstoppable and Untargetable while leaping to the lowest Armor enemy.

skill.name: Sporecloud Dart
skill.desc:
Fire a dart that explodes into a cloud of spores, poisoning nearby enemies in 1-hex area. Poisoned enemies take 340/510/765(%i:scaleAP%) over 4/5/6 seconds and are Blinded for 4/5/6 seconds.

Blind: Attack might miss

skill.name: Rapid Fire
skill.desc: Gain 60/65/70% Attack Speed. Attacks deal 40/60/80(%i:scaleAP%) bonus magic damage for 3 seconds.

skill.name: Spinning Slash
skill.desc: Spin in a line towards the most enemies possible within 4 hexes, dealing 120/180/270(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to enemies in the path and empowering the next 3 attacks to deal 64/128/383(%i:TFTBaseAD%) bonus physical damage.

skill.name: Wild Cards
skill.desc: Throw 3 cards in a cone toward a random target within range, dealing 180/270/400(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to each enemy they pass through.

skill.name: Dark Blossom
skill.desc:
Blast the enemy with the lowest Health in range, dealing 400/600/900(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage.

If the target dies, permanently gain 1/2/3 Ability Power.

skill.name: Denting Blow
skill.desc:
Deal 225/375/575(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to all enemies in a cone toward the current target and Sunder them by 20/30/50% for 8 seconds.

Sunder: Reduce Armor

skill.name: Transfusion
skill.desc: Deal 350/525/790(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to the target. All allies within 2-hex radius are healed for 50% of the damage dealt.

skill.name: Crushing Blow
skill.desc: Slam the target with a staff, dealing 170/270/465(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage and Stunning them for 1.5/2/3 seconds.

skill.name: Featherstorm
skill.desc:
Leap into the air and become Untargetable and Invulnerable, throwing a fan of 9 feather daggers in a cone towards the current target that deal 170/290/480(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to enemies they pass through.

After a brief delay, recall feathers, striking enemies hit for 100/200/600(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage per feather.

skill.name: Striking Steel
skill.desc: Strike forward 2 hexes, dealing 135/205/305(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to enemies hit. If 2 enemies wouldn't be hit by this, attempt to dash to a better position.

skill.name: Seal Fate
skill.desc:
Strike along a path towards the current target, dealing 725/1050/15000(%i:scaleAP%) split between all enemies hit. Enemies hit are marked for death and are Sundered and Shredded for 40/40/50% for 8 seconds.
This Ability becomes Unforgotten until no enemies are marked for death.

Unforgotten (10 mana): Dash to the lowest-Health enemy marked for death, dealing 275/600/9999(%i:scaleAP%) plus 10% of their missing health as magic damage.

Sunder: Reduce Armor
Shred: Reduce Magic Resist

skill.name: Zoomies
skill.desc: Dash to the lowest-Health ally, healing for 30%/40%/50%(%i:scaleAP%) of missing Health and granting 30%/40%/60%(%i:scaleAP%) Attack Speed for 5 seconds. Repeat this on the farthest ally.

skill.name: Contempt For The Weak
skill.desc:
Innate: At the start of combat, jump to the enemy backline.

Passive: Every third attack deals 30/60/90(%i:scaleAP%) bonus magic damage and steals 25/30/35% of the target's current Attack Damage.

skill.name: Rewind Fate
skill.desc: Place a protective Time Rune on 2/3/10 allies with the lowest Health (excluding self). If they die, they resurrect after 3/2/0.5 seconds with 400/600/3000(%i:scaleAP%) Health and shed all negative effects. After resurrecting, they gain 60%/85%/1500%(%i:scaleAP%) Attack Speed for the rest of combat.

skill.name: The Show Stopper
skill.desc: Grab target and slam them forward, dealing 220/350/9999(%i:scaleAP%) + 3%/9%/900%(%i:scaleAP%) of their max Health as magic damage to them. All other enemies within 3 hexes take 50% of the total damage.

skill.name: Stand United
skill.desc: Grant 250/325/425(%i:scaleAP%) Shield to this unit and a nearby damaged ally for 4 seconds.

skill2.name: Shadow Dash
skill2.desc: Dash to the lowest Health enemy within 3 hexes, dealing 92/138/207(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage. This effect happens 3 times, increased by 1 per cast.

skill.name: Dragon's Descent / Flame Breath
skill.desc:
Dragon's Descent: Transform into a dragon, gaining 600/1000/9999 max Health. Briefly gain 20/20/90% Durability and dive-bomb into the largest group of enemies, dealing 100/150/3000(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage in a 3 hex circle.

Flame Breath: Breath fire in a cone for 3 seconds, dealing 205/305/13579(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage each second to enemies hit.

skill.name: Poison Trail
skill.desc:
Passive: Run around the battlefield, leaving a poison trail that lingers for 4 seconds. Poison trails deal 8/18/160(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage per second to enemies within. Gain 4(%i:scaleAS%) Mana each second.

Active: For 4 seconds, gain increased Move Speed, restore 15/80/500(%i:scaleAP%) Health each second, and gain 20 Armor and Magic Resistance.

skill.name: Soul Furnace
skill.desc:
Passive: Takedowns grant 18/20/50 permanent max Health. (Total: ?)

Active: Gain 226/272/334(%i:scaleHealth%%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 4 seconds. When it breaks, deal 26/47/84(%i:scaleHealth%) magic damage to adjacent enemies.

skill.name: Impale
skill.desc:
Passive: All allies gain 10/20/100 Armor.

Active: Gain 750/950/3000(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 4 seconds. Impale up to three nearby enemies in a line, dealing 84/126/1750(%i:scaleArmor%) physical damage and Stunning them for 1.5/1.75/8 seconds.

skill.name: Power Chord
skill.desc: Deal 130/195/300(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to 2 nearby enemies and restore 30/40/65(%i:scaleAP%) Health to the lowest Health ally.

skill.name: Nevermove
skill.desc:
Passive: Each second, restore 36/52/158(%i:scaleHealth%%i:scaleAP%) Health and deal 20/30/90(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies within 1 Hex.

Active: Open a demonic eye on the largest group of nearby enemies, dealing 100/150/1800(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage and Stunning them for 1.5/1.75/8 seconds.

skill.name: Stolen Might
skill.desc:
Cast one of three spells:

Cataclysm: Leap on a nearby enemy. Deal 120/200/1000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to all enemies within 2 hexes and Stun them for 1.5 seconds.

Demacian Justice: Deal 700/1050/99999(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to target. If they are below 15% max Health, execute them.

Final Spark: Gain 400/450/800(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 1.25 seconds. Deal 300/475/1000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to all enemies in a line.

skill.name: Devour
skill.desc:
Devour target for 2.5 seconds, dealing 1200/1800/30000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage and making them immune to other sources of damage. During this time, gain 30% Durability. If they are immune to crowd control, deal 1000/1500/20000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage instead.

If they die while devoured, spit out a random component they were holding or the unit's cost in gold. Otherwise, spit them towards the farthest enemy, briefly Stunning targets on impact.

skill.name: Starlight's Touch
skill.desc:
Passive: All allies gain 10/20/100 Magic Resist. Once per combat after dropping below 35% max Health, restore 300/700/2500 health over 2 seconds.

Active: Gain 600/700/2500(%i:scaleAP%) Shield and grant the 2 lowest Health allies 125/150/1000(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 4 seconds. The next 2/2/10 attacks deal 200/300/3000(%i:scaleAP%) bonus magic damage.

skill.name: Toxic Dart
skill.desc: Shoot the closest unpoisoned enemy, dealing 130/200/330(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage and poisoning them for 8 seconds. Poisoned enemies take 35/55/100(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage each second.

skill.name: Hextech Arsenal
skill.desc:
Passive: Attacks fire a barrage of 4 bullets.

Active: Gain 440/652/67120(%i:scaleHealth%) Shield and begin consuming 33 mana per second. Each second while casting, fire a laser that deals 170/280/2150(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage, reduced by 35% per enemy hit up to 80%. Additionally, launch 4(%i:scaleAS%) missiles split between 4 nearby enemies that each deal 34/56/430(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage.

skill.name: The Box
skill.desc:
Passive: Each second, deal 30/50/400(%i:scaleAP%%i:scaleSouls%) magic damage to all enemies within 2 hexes. Heal for 75% of the damage dealt by this effect.

Active: Create a prison of walls in a 2 hex radius that lasts 5 seconds. While active, the Passive's damage is doubled. When an enemy touches a wall, they take 100/150/4000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage. If there are less than 2 enemies inside The Box at any time, drag an enemy in.

skill.name: Rage of Embers
skill.desc:
Passive: After attacking an enemy, restore 38/68/4860(%i:scaleHealth%) Health. If they are Burning, the healing is doubled.

Active: Gain 200/200/500% Attack Speed and 1000/1200/9000(%i:scaleAP%) Shield that decays over 4 seconds. Gain immunity to Crowd Control effects for the same duration.

Burn: Deal 1% of the target's max Health as true damage every second

skill.name: Buster Shot
skill.desc: Fire a massive cannonball at target, dealing 280/420/670(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage. If they are within 2 hexes, knock them back 2 hexes and briefly Stun them.

skill.name: Undying Rage
skill.desc:
Become enraged for 5 seconds. While enraged, gain 15%(%i:scaleAP%) Durability and attacks are replaced with a strike that deals 110/160/235(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage. Ignore 30% of Armor against Chilled enemies.

Bloodsworn Bond: When you field Ashe and Tryndamere, your strongest copies permanently increase their power on kill.
Bloodsworn Bond: Gain increased Move Speed. Gain 10% Attack Damage, permanently increased by 1% whenever Ashe or Tryndamere score a kill. (Current Bonus: 10%)

Chill: Reduce Attack Speed

skill.name: Stacked Deck
skill.desc:
Passive: Attacks deal 50/75/115(%i:scaleAP%) bonus magic damage. After every 3rd attack, throw 3 cards in a cone that deal 70/105/160(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage, reduced by 50% for each enemy they pass through.

Partners in Crime: When you field Graves and Twisted Fate, both gain bonuses.
Partners in Crime: Twisted Fate's ability marks targets for Graves. When Graves kills a marked target, gain 10% Ability Power until end of combat.

skill.name: Tumble
skill.desc: Tumble to a nearby hex, then fire a bolt at target that deals 106/160/245(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) true damage.

skill.name: Dark Storm
skill.desc:
Passive: Gain 50% more Ability Power from all sources.

Active: Call down a storm of 12/12/24 meteors across the battlefield that deal 62/93/199(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage each. They can innately critically strike. For each one that kills an enemy, permanently gain 1 Ability Power.

skill.name: Relentless Force
skill.desc: Gain 125/150/175(%i:scaleAP%) Shield for 2 seconds. Slam on target, dealing 120/180/270(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to enemies in a 1 hex range. Every third cast deals 150/225/340(%i:scaleAD%) damage in a 2 hex range instead and knocks up enemies hit for 1 second.

skill.name: Blade of the Ruined King
skill.desc:
Passive: Gain 10%(%i:scaleSouls%) Attack Speed.

Active: Deal 55/85/125(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to target. For the rest of combat, Viego's attacks deal 18/27/42(%i:scaleAP%) bonus stacking magic damage.

skill2.name: Blade of the Ruined King
skill2.desc:
Passive: Gain 10%(%i:scaleSouls%) Attack Speed.

Active: Leap to the largest group of enemies within 2-hexes, dealing 280/420/630(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage split between adjacent enemies + 100/150/230(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to each. For the rest of combat, Viego's attacks deal 48/72/108(%i:scaleAP%) bonus stacking magic damage.

skill.name: The Relentless Storm
skill.desc:
Bite the target and mark them, dealing 136/215/2117(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleHealth%) physical damage, increased by 60% if they are already marked. After casting 5 times, leap to a nearby hex, activating Stormbringer and dealing 272/430/4233(%i:scaleHealth%%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to enemies within a two hex radius.

Stormbringer: Gain 400/550/9999 Health and 50/50/999% Attack Speed. Every 2 seconds, summon a lightning bolt on a nearby enemy, dealing 98/161/1155(%i:scaleHealth%%i:scaleAP%) magic damage. Takedowns summon a bolt on fallen enemies.

skill.name: Eternal Hunger
skill.desc: Gain 100/100/400% Attack Speed, 15% Omnivamp, increased Move Speed, and deal 45/70/550(%i:scaleAD%) bonus physical damage on attack for the rest of combat. While this effect is active, takedowns grant Warwick, Jinx, and Vi 20%/20%/50%(%i:scaleAP%) Attack Speed for 3 seconds.

skill.name: Diverting Trickster
skill.desc:
Passive: On death, summon a Stone copy with 570/956/3361(%i:scaleHealth%) Health and Wukong's items.

Active: For 4 seconds, gain 100/110/400(%i:scaleAP%) Armor and Magic Resist. Then spin, dealing 150/225/3000(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage to all enemies within 2 hexes.

skill.name: Eye of the Ascendant
skill.desc: Launch 10 arcane blasts randomly split between the closest 4 enemies that each deal 390/650/2500(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage.

skill.name: Three Talon Strike
skill.desc: Strike target 3 times. Each strike deals 65/100/150(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage and restores 105/145/200(%i:scaleAP%) Health. The final one Stuns for 1.5 seconds.

skill2.name: Wind Becomes Lightning
skill2.desc: Begin losing 20% max Mana each second. Constantly slash, dealing 155/235/345(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage each second to enemies hit. If any enemies within 2 hexes are below 15% Health, briefly stop slashing and execute them, then restore 8 mana.

skill.name: Sweeping Blade
skill.desc:
Dash, then deal 93/137/208(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to adjacent enemies. If only one enemy is hit, deal double damage.

Blade Brothers: When you field Yasuo and Yone, Yasuo assists Yone's casts.
Blade Brothers: When Yone casts, your strongest Yasuo blinks to every target Yone hits and deals 100% %i:TFTBaseAD% physical damage to each.

skill.name: Kin of the Stained Blade
skill.desc:
Passive: Attacks alternate between dealing 80/120/800(%i:scaleAD%) bonus physical damage and 140/210/1400(%i:scaleAP%) bonus magic damage.

Active: Strike through the most enemies possible within 3 hexes, knocking them up for 1.5 seconds and dealing 80/120/480(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage and 80/120/480(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) magic damage. Yone then splits 320/480/2160(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage and 320/480/2160(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) magic damage among all enemies hit.

Blade Brothers: When you field Yasuo and Yone, Yasuo assists Yone's casts.
Blade Brothers: When Yone casts, your strongest Yasuo blinks to each target, dealing bonus physical damage.

skill.name: Mourning Mist
skill.desc:
Restore 325/370/500(%i:scaleAP%%i:scaleSouls%) Health. Throw a globule of black mist at the enemy who has dealt the most damage this combat, preferring unique enemies. It 20% Chills them for 4 seconds and raises the Mana cost of their next cast by 20. It then deals 123/187/288(%i:scaleHealth%) magic damage in 1 hex radius.

Chill: Reduce Attack Speed

skill.name: Transcendent State
skill.desc: For the next 4 seconds, gain 65%/65%/300%(%i:scaleAP%) Attack Speed, infinite range, and replace attacks with lasers. Lasers deal 80/120/425(%i:scaleAD%) physical damage in a line, reduced by 75% for each enemy they pass through. When lasers critically strike, they deal 33% bonus true damage.

skill.name: Divine Challenge
skill.desc:
Dash around target and slash in a circle, dealing 110/165/1700(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to target and 44/66/680(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to all other adjacent enemies hit. If the target doesn't die, immediately cast again.

If this Ability is cast 22 times in a row, instead slam on target, instantly killing them and dealing 220/330/3400(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) physical damage to all enemies within 3 hexes.

skill.name: Mega Inferno Bomb
skill.desc:
Passive: Attacks are replaced with a bomb that bounces 1 time, dealing 40/65/500(%i:scaleAD%%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to units hit.

Active: Throw an enormous bomb at the largest 4-hex group of enemies that explodes on impact, dealing between 70/105/3000(%i:scaleAP%) and 550/875/7000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage to enemies hit based on their distance from the epicenter.

skill.name: Visions of the End
skill.desc:
Throw a Time Bomb on the nearest enemy without one. Time Bombs deal 75/115/1000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage each second. When the target dies, they explode, dealing 150/225/4000(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage in a 1 hex radius and grant Zilean 15 mana.

If a Time Bomb is on an enemy for 18/16/1 seconds and Zilean is alive, the enemy instantly dies.

skill.name: Double Trouble Bubble
skill.desc:
Passive: Damaging an enemy applies 30% Shred for 6 seconds.

Active: Kick 2 bubbles at nearby enemies, dealing 330/500/770(%i:scaleAP%) magic damage and 30% Chilling them for 2 seconds.

Shred: Reduce Magic Resist
Chill: Reduce Attack Speed
